      "description": "Offered is an analog masterpiece: a BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This driver-spec example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to deliver power to the rear wheels via a factory-equipped limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to maintain precise variable valve timing. The engine pulls strongly through its individual throttle bodies with no hesitation. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical components are tuned for peak performance. A well-sorted chassis for the discerning enthusiast seeking a pure longitudinal-engine, rear-drive experience.",
