      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in a stunning Deep Sea Blue Metallic finish. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep shine, though it shows minor, expected stone chips on the front fascia from highway commuting. Inside, the Ivory White Dakota leather remains supple and clean, housed in a cabin that has never seen pets or smoke. Every feature, from the panoramic glass sunroof to the premium Harman Kardon surround sound, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this SUV is robust; it comes with a comprehensive service history, showing regular oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. The turbocharged inline-six engine delivers smooth, effortless power, and the xDrive all-wheel-drive system provides confidence in all weather conditions. It currently sits on Continental tires with significant tread depth remaining. This is a solid, reliable, and well-cared-for example ready for its next owner.",
